thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by kim Mclean

author: kim Mclean
title: kim Mclean
text:
I accidentally stumbled on Ink Station and thought why not. Their prices were very competitive and i wasn't sure when i would have time to make it to the shops.
The ordering online was streamline and simple and 2 days later my ink was delivered. I can not fault Ink station in any way. I will never go and buy ink anywhere else, i mean why would you?
